### RULES
### === MUST COME BEFORE CONFIG ===

# See https://github.com/koekeishiya/yabai/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#removed
yabai -m rule --add app!="^(Google Chrome|Code|Safari|WhatsApp|Telegram A)$" manage=off
yabai -m rule --apply


### CONFIG

yabai -m config top_padding    6
yabai -m config bottom_padding 6
yabai -m config left_padding   6
yabai -m config right_padding  6
yabai -m config window_gap     8

yabai -m config mouse_modifier ctrl

yabai -m config layout bsp

$HOME/Documents/Playground/JankyBorders/bin/borders active_color=0xff169fff inactive_color=0xff1f252c width=5.0 &
